The purpose of this article is to report on the long-term clinical evaluation of 
patients treated with dental implants. A total of 106 implants were placed in 34 
patients and restored with fixed partial dentures and overdentures. The 12-year 
cumulative implant survival and success rates were 95.2% and 90.2%, 
